your femoral artery there.

2195
02:42:42,290 --> 02:42:44,326
Why, you're gonna
bleed to death, huh?

2196
02:42:45,259 --> 02:42:47,829
[groaning]

2197
02:42:47,862 --> 02:42:50,431
-[Rose grunting]
-[choking]

2198
02:42:50,464 --> 02:42:52,901
