02:42:57,939 --> 02:43:00,008
-[flesh squelching]
-[screaming]

2203
02:43:03,211 --> 02:43:05,013
[inhaling]

2204
02:43:05,046 --> 02:43:07,282
Oh, damn.

2205
02:43:07,315 --> 02:43:09,851
