2209
02:43:19,627 --> 02:43:21,396
[inhaling]

2210
02:43:24,031 --> 02:43:25,133
[Jack] Danny!

2211
02:43:26,167 --> 02:43:27,435
Danny boy!

2212
02:43:28,936 --> 02:43:31,039
Oh, so much terror.

2213
02:43:31,072 --> 02:43:32,941
